<div class="panel">
<p>Human resources or HR are the set of the people who make up the workforce of an organisation, business sector, industry, or economy. A narrower concept is human capital, the knowledge which the individuals embody. Similar terms include manpower, labour, personnel, associates or simply people.</p>
