<button class="accordion">What is HR management?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>HR Management is the strategic approach to the effective management of people in a company or organisation such that they help their business gain a competitive advantage. This design is to help maximise employee performance in the service of an employer's strategic objectives.</p>
